          <div class="day-item"><div class="day-num">4</div><div class="day-info"><strong>Kikelewa → Mawenzi Tarn Hut (Acclimatization)</strong><span>3,600m → 4,330m &bull; Dramatic Mawenzi Peak views</span></div></div>
          <div class="day-item"><div class="day-num">5</div><div class="day-info"><strong>Mawenzi Tarn → Kibo Hut</strong><span>4,330m → 4,703m &bull; Cross the Saddle between peaks</span></div></div>
